ComputerCraft was created by Daniel "dan200" Ratcliffe (@DanTwoHundred on twitter). Monitors were based on code by Cloudy (@Cloudhunter).
Thanks to everyone in #computercraft on irc.esper.net who helped with testing and support. Thanks to Casper7526 and Kane_Hart for setting up the website.
Thanks to Eloraam for permission to interface with RedPower2.
Uses LuaJ from http://luaj.sourceforge.net/
Uses LuaBit from http://luaforge.net/projects/bit/

Join the ComputerCraft community online at http://www.computercraft.info, and share your creations and programs!
